<li id="cite_note-259"><b><a href="#cite_ref-259" title="">^</a></b> Mark Humphries, "Constantine," review of <i>Constantine and the Christian Empire</i>, by Charles Odahl, <i>Classical Quarterly</i> 56:2 (2006), 449.</li>
<li id="cite_note-260"><b><a href="#cite_ref-260" title="">^</a></b> Averil Cameron, "Introduction," in <i>Constantine: History, Historiography, and Legend</i>, ed. Samuel N.C. Lieu and Dominic Montserrat (New York: Routledge, 1998), 3.</li>
